          "text": "if %compileResult.Cached% is true, call /system/builder/EmitBuildEvent kind=\"step-cached\", step=%step%",
          "lineNumber": 81,
          "indent": 0,
          "comment": "Per-step build summary line, plus a warning line when either the planner or\nthe compiler reported Low / VeryLow confidence (LLM had to settle for a\nfallback action or guess a mapping \u2014 the dev should see it at build time).",
          "actions": [
